OL,3,CHospitals and police stations set for
OL,4,Ctax hikes in business rates overhaul
OL,6,FHundreds of NHS hospitals,
OL,7,Funiversities and police stations will
OL,8,Fface a new Government levy under an
OL,9,F"ill-thought-out" overhaul of business
OL,10,Frates rules, according to a new
OL,11,Fanalysis.
OL,13,FThe Government said in Wednesday's
OL,14,Fautumn Budget that it would make a
OL,15,Fraft of changes to the current regime
OL,16,Ffor business rates, the tax on
OL,17,Fcommercial properties, in order to
OL,18,Fease the burden on smaller high street
OL,19,Foperators.
