OL,3,CHospitals and police stations set for
OL,4,Ctax hikes in business rates overhaul
OL,6,FIt said it would permanently lower the
OL,7,Fbusiness rates multipliers for high
OL,8,Fstreet retail, hospitality and leisure
OL,9,Fbusiness premises with a rateable
OL,10,Fvalue of less than #500,000 from 2026.
OL,12,FIt is part of efforts from politicians
OL,13,Fto change the balance in tax payments
OL,14,Fbetween bricks and mortar high street
OL,15,Ffirms and online competitors.
OL,17,FBusiness rates bills are calculated by
OL,18,Fmultiplying the property's rateable
OL,19,Fvalue, an estimate of open market
OL,20,Frent, by figures set by the Government
OL,21,Feach year.
