OL,3,CHospitals and police stations set for
OL,4,Ctax hikes in business rates overhaul
OL,6,FThe multiplier figures depend on the
OL,7,Fvalue of the property, with ratepayers
OL,8,Fpaying the multiplier amount for every
OL,9,F#1 of rateable value.
OL,11,FIn order to provide this tax cut for
OL,12,Fsome firms, the Treasury has said it
OL,13,Fwill introduce a new rate on more
OL,14,Fvaluable commercial properties.
OL,16,FProperties with a rateable value of
OL,17,F#500,000 or more will face a new
OL,18,Fhigher multiplier.
