OL,3,CHospitals and police stations set for
OL,4,Ctax hikes in business rates overhaul
OL,6,FThe Government said this will include
OL,7,Fthe majority of large distribution
OL,8,Fwarehouses used by online businesses
OL,9,Fsuch as Amazon.
OL,11,FAnalysis of official Government data
OL,12,Fby Altus Group found that this new
OL,13,Fhigh street "levy" will apply to 1,589
OL,14,Flarge distribution warehouses.
OL,16,FHowever, it found this will also lead
OL,17,Fto higher business rates bills for a
OL,18,Ffurther additional 15,278 non-domestic
OL,19,Fproperties too.
