OL,3,CHospitals and police stations set for
OL,4,Ctax hikes in business rates overhaul
OL,6,FThe analysis found that 297 NHS
OL,7,FHospitals will be subject to the new
OL,8,F"levy" including major hospitals such
OL,9,Fas the Royal London Hospital, Royal
OL,10,FDerby Hospital, Bristol's Southmead
OL,11,FHospital.
OL,13,FAdditionally, 310 universities and 309
OL,14,Ffurther education colleges will also
OL,15,Fface the levy as well as 10 properties
OL,16,Fused by the Metropolitan Police
OL,17,FService including New Scotland Yard.
