OL,3,CHospitals and police stations set for
OL,4,Ctax hikes in business rates overhaul
OL,6,FOver 200 Government properties from
OL,7,Fmilitary barracks to court buildings
OL,8,Fto prisons will also face the
OL,9,Fincrease, the data showed.
OL,11,FIt is not yet known how large the
OL,12,Fincrease will be to the multiplier and
OL,13,Ftherefore how large the tax increase
OL,14,Fwill be for these properties and their
OL,15,Foperators.
OL,17,FAlex Probyn, president of property tax
OL,18,Fat Altus Group, said that the plan had
OL,19,Fbeen "ill-thought-out".
